version_description: Added missing chords to each verse.
Includes chords and diagrams for special inversions.
Complete chords for the whole song / intermediate with split chords / suggestions for playable voicings / short tabs for instrumental parts.
Complete lyrics and backing vocals all with accompanying chords and bass notes, also tablature for the coda.
Asus4 can be played on the "yeah" of the chorus. the intro can be repeated during the A minor parts of the verse and chorus.
All lyrics have accompanying chords, chords with bass note progressions, additional info with tablature riffs and more chord options.
Added intro tab to this version.
